ter velocities at larger radii\nare needed to further study the low rotation in the globular cluster system,\nand to see if the dark matter halo in M104 extends beyond a radius of 30 kpc.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 29 Nov 2006 19:44:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-24"}
